00:15:21.310 --> 00:15:24.170
and he has made that
famous national anthem

00:15:24.170 --> 00:15:26.660
of Iran, the people, [inaudible].

00:15:26.660 --> 00:15:28.570
So I went to Iran.

00:15:28.570 --> 00:15:31.490
We looked at it and he
